---

<Layout>
  <section id="hero-section">
    <!-- <Picture
      class="hero-shot"
      src={heroImg}
      alt="Unitree Go2-W "
      loading="eager"
      fetchpriority={"high"}
      quality={"high"}
    /> -->
    <video
      playsinline
      muted
      loop
      preload="metadata"
      width=""
      height=""
      class="hero-shot media"
    >
      <source src="/videos/r1/1.mp4" type="video/mp4" />
    </video>

    <div class="content">
      <h1 class="h1">Unitree Go2-W</h1>
      <p class="subtitle-3">Transformative Newborn</p>
    </div>
    <div class="sub-content">
      <h1 class="h1 text-center">
        The Ultra-Lightweight, Highly Accessible <br /> Humanoid Robot
      </h1>
      <span class="paragraph-1">
        The Unitree R1 offers an intelligent, open, and flexible platform at an
        unprecedented price point, making advanced humanoid robotics accessible
        to all.
      </span>

      <!-- <ButtonPrimary content="Buy now" type="a" href={pages.product.path} /> -->
    </div>
  </section>
  <section id="new-section">
    <!-- <div class="content">
      <div class="line-element">
        <div></div>
        <span> Wheeled Legged Robot Dog</span>
        <div></div>
      </div>
      <h2 class="h1 text-center">Go2 New Model</h2>
      <p>Transformative Newborn</p>
    </div> -->
    <div class="shot">
      <Picture
        src={modelShot}
        alt={"Go2 New Model "}
        fetchpriority={"high"}
        quality={"max"}
      />
      <div class="detail">
        <p>Price starting from <br /> $4,900 (R1 AIR)</p>
        <span> Affordability </span>
        <img src="/images/indicator.svg" alt="" loading="lazy" />
      </div>
      <div class="detail">
        <p>Integrated with Large <br /> Multimodal Model</p>
        <span>Intelligence</span>
        <img src="/images/indicator.svg" alt="" loading="lazy" />
      </div>
      <div class="detail">
        <p>Ultra-lightweight <br /> (~29kg)</p>
        <span> Design </span>
        <img src="/images/indicator.svg" alt="" loading="lazy" />
      </div>
      <div class="detail">
        <p>20-26 Degrees of <br /> Freedom</p>
        <span> Agility</span>
        <img src="/images/indicator.svg" alt="" loading="lazy" />
      </div>
    </div>

    <Image class={"blue-shade"} src={blue_shade} alt={""} format="webp" />
  </section>
  <section class="shot-section flex-start-row">
    <video
      playsinline
      muted
      loop
      preload="metadata"
      width=""
      height=""
      class="media"
    >
      <source src="/videos/r1/2.mp4" type="video/mp4" />
    </video>
    <div class="content">
      <h2 class="h1">
        High Agility in a <br /> Lightweight Design
      </h2>
      <p class="paragraph-1">
        The R1 is designed to be ultra-lightweight, with the R1 model weighing
        approximately 29kg. Despite its size, it features 20-26 Degrees of
        Freedom (DOF), allowing it to perform complex movements and adapt to
        various scenarios. Its 2-DOF head enhances perception, and its compact
        form factor makes it ideal for indoor environments and educational
        settings.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
  <section class="shot-section flex-end-row">
    <video
      playsinline
      muted
      loop
      preload="metadata"
      width=""
      height=""
      class="media"
    >
      <source src="/videos/r1/3.mp4" type="video/mp4" />
    </video>
    <div class="content">
      <h2 class="h1">Integrated with Large <br /> Multimodal Model</h2>
      <p class="paragraph-1">
        The R1 is an intelligent agent, integrated with a Large Multimodal Model
        for voice and image processing. This allows for advanced interaction and
        decision-making, positioning the R1 as an ideal platform for developing
        next-generation AI applications and personal assistants.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
  <section class="shot-section flex-start-row flex-align-start">
    <Picture class={"shot"} src={dev} alt="Open Platform" />
    <div class="content">
      <h2 class="h1">Open Platform for Development</h2>
      <p class="paragraph-1">
        The R1 is highly focused on development and research. It offers fully
        open control interfaces for all joints and sensors, supporting
        mainstream simulation platforms. The R1 EDU model provides an optional
        NVIDIA Jetson Orin computing core, offering up to 100 TOPS of processing
        power for advanced custom applications.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
  <section class="shot-section flex-end-row last-elem">
    <video
      playsinline
      muted
      loop
      preload="metadata"
      width=""
      height=""
      class="media"
    >
      <source src="/videos/r1/4.mp4" type="video/mp4" />
    </video>
    <div class="content">
      <h2 class="h1">Essential Technical <br /> Specifications</h2>
      <p class="paragraph-1">
        The R1 (EDU) is equipped with a Binocular Camera for sensing and has an
        arm capable of carrying a 2kg load. Its battery provides approximately 1
        hour of endurance, making it suitable for focused development and
        demonstration sessions.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="tech-section">
    <!-- <Picture src={specs} alt={"Technical specifications"} /> -->

    <div class="table">
      <div class="head">
        <div class="line-element big-desktop">
          <div></div>
          <span> r1 </span>
          <div></div>
        </div>
        <h2 class="h1">Technical Specifications</h2>
      </div>

      <table class="robot-spec-table">
        <thead>
          <tr>
            <th>Characteristic</th>
            <th>R1</th>
            <th>r1 EDU</th>
          </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr>
            <td>Weight (with battery)</td>
            <td>18kg</td>
            <td>Highly portable for a wheeled-legged robot.</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>Payload (Max)</td>
            <td>8kg (MAX ~ 12kg)</td>
            <td>Suitable for various sensors and payloads.</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>Speed Range</td>
            <td>0 - 2.5 m/s</td>
            <td>Efficient wheeled movement and dynamic legged motion.</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>Endurance</td>
            <td>1.5 - 3h (15000mAh battery)</td>
            <td>Varies based on mode of locomotion and load.</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>Max Joint Torque</td>
            <td>45 N.m</td>
            <td>Ensures responsive and stable movement.</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>Obstacle Crossing</td>
            <td>Up to 70cm</td>
            <td>Superior capability for overcoming large obstacles.</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>Sensing</td>
            <td>3D LiDAR + HD Wide-angle Camera</td>
            <td>Advanced environmental awareness.</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>Computing</td>
            <td>8-core CPU, Orin NX optional</td>
            <td>Powerful core for AI and development.</td>
          </tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>
    </div>
  </section>
  <section class="cards-section">
    <h2 class="h2">
      Enhance Your R1 <br class="br-mobile br-tablet" /> Development Platform
    </h2>
    <div class="cards">
